title New note SPA

note over browser:
browser creates a note from input
value and browser date when form
is submitted, pushes it to the notes
array and redraws all the notes.
Finally, sends the new note to the server
in the next request
end note
browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
note over server:
server creates a new note object
from request payload and adds it
to the array of notes (?)
end note
server-->browser: JSON-code: {"message":"note created"}
